author: Hero Hei
description:
Genshin Impact VA for Paimon went on air claiming that she told Hoyo she would not voice as Paimon any further unless they signed a union contract. Many people are celebrating this news as Paimon may be replaced but many are also reasonably very skeptical that Paimon Eng VA is telling the truth about what happened.
